Comment: 0,0:00:38.48,0:00:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k282}哪里的歌 {\k342}宁可直往忿怨的道路?
Comment: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k276}一到夜晚 {\k384}那温度该往去哪条路?
Comment: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k322}孤独伴我 {\k304}孤单执念真模糊悲痛!
Comment: 0,0:00:57.58,0:01:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k268}寂寞孤零 {\k180}迈步入 {\k244}高歌落幕的最晚之时
Comment: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k124}跨过这坡道 {\k126}漆黑一生
Comment: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,歌谣遗下一堆念叫『累』的哄闹
Comment: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k174}无顾虑舞动的 {\k132}苦恋是名为
Comment: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,『每战伴酸涩的常有伤』
Comment: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k150}于密室的阁楼 {\k134}复古的墙壁
Comment: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,谁能够合为散乱的木料?
Comment: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k166}每次恸哭 {\k160}没际遇的
Comment: 0,0:01:26.40,0:01:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,伤痕特别的多
Comment: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,It's so far away！
Comment: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,哀歌祈祷一样
Comment: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k220}我为您留念 {\k277}默默砍断迷茫 {\k171}最终归土
Comment: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k356}看那耀目的 {\k288}生命一味凋落
Comment: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可能也该遗忘?
Comment: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k180}亦可令我 {\k288}打开虚拟的大门
Comment: 0,0:01:55.12,0:02:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k274}但请我的爱 {\k230}跨过古老
Comment: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,唯独使手中那泪滴 归零......
Comment: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k312}而心游动 {\k306}宽敞的云谷里游浮
Comment: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k228}难耐够了 {\k456}直到唯有跨过那透明的路
Comment: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k116}无奈以演绎 {\k128}恳挚此刻要
Comment: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,为了可能如还能顽固地般另觅
Comment: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k132}那名为痛苦的 {\k124}大雨随着落
Comment: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,『能感悟而爱恋的寓意』
Comment: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k176}瞳孔里的暴怒 {\k160}只有你淡忘了
Comment: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我一直默默渴望你亦如
Comment: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,绝不对恶魔般的
Comment: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,茫惘埋怨不能
Comment: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,Starting over!
Comment: 0,0:02:57.76,0:03:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,直到夜晚也要
Comment: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k248}惦记那矛盾是 {\k242}污蔑的渴望路
Comment: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如刀一样 
