Comment: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k196}其实轻歌雅柔 {\k344}如同伴你
Comment: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k246}与歌声于朦胧 {\k362}一同来到宁远的岛
Comment: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k244}只可待声音闪过 {\k196}有你在的黑白路
Comment: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一生如悲
Comment: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k272}回头只能悲痛着 {\k336}那广阔夺目时代
Comment: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k308}是如她的哀念歌声 {\k620}守望
Comment: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,It's so far away!
